snippet.title: Twin Stones: The journey of Bukka - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Twin Stones: The journey of Bukka is an upcoming challenging 3D platformer with pretty astonishing scenarios. You play as Bukka, a young hunter with the help of Shiva, the God of Destruction.

This project has been made by students in ESAT Valencia with the collaboration of Berklee College of Music.

Twitter account: https://twitter.com/TwinStones
